OL,3,CThings really do seem better in the
OL,4,Cmorning, scientists say
OL,6,FPeople in the study answered
OL,7,Fquestionnaires, including questions
OL,8,Fsuch as: "In the past week, how happy
OL,9,Fdid you feel?", "How satisfied have
OL,10,Fyou been with your life?", and "To
OL,11,Fwhat extent have you felt the things
OL,12,Fyou are doing in your life are
OL,13,Fworthwhile?"
OL,15,FFactors such as age, health conditions
OL,16,Fand whether people worked were taken
OL,17,Finto account.
